1) Find a mob that doesn't hit for much but has lots of health.<br>
2) Get a friend and have him build up lots of aggro on a mob.<br>
3) Have the friend stand there getting hit without fighting back.<br>
4) Nuke the mob until you gain aggro.<br>
5) Nuke the mob once more to make sure you have firm aggro.<br>
6) Cast concussion a couple times.<br>
7) Watch the mob turn back on your friend.<br>
8)  Repeat steps 4 through 7, each time watching that the mob turns on your friend right after Concussion hits or is resisted.<br>
